==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inhalant
<hw>In*hal"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>inhalant</ets>.]</ety> <def>Inhaling; used for inhaling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inhalant</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Inhalant
<hw>In*hal"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An apparatus also
called an <altname>inhaler</altname> (which see); also, that which is to
be inhaled, especially a medicine taken by inhalation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inhalation</ent>⟦br⟧
